Class MessageJsonReconstructionTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.linecorp.bot.model.message.MessageJsonReconstructionTest

  • public class MessageJsonReconstructionTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Message object reconstruction test.

    This is not a part of SDK SPEC but please check it is expected/unavoidable or not when any test is broken.

    IMPORTANT: Message serialization/deserialization by JSON is to be able to create a proof of concept in simple. This test do not intended serialization format stability. Serialized JSON format may be different depending on the version.
